id: pm-xy02
title: MCP pm_context crashes on caller-supplied projection flags (compact/brief/fields/includeBody)
description: "Fixed: pm_context downstream passes options to runList; if caller supplies compact/brief/fields/includeBody, the list returns the compact projection (id/status/type/title only) and runContext's toContextFocusItem chokes with `item.tags is not iterable`.\n\nRoot cause: context.ts forwards full options dict to runList without stripping projection flags.\n\nFix: src/cli/commands/context.ts — added stripListProjectionFlags() helper that removes compact/brief/fields/includeBody/include_body before forwarding, applied to both the list query and calendar query. Also hardened toContextFocusItem() to default tags to [] when missing. Added regression test in tests/unit/context-command.spec.ts.\n\nSeverity: blocking — any MCP caller passing common projection options gets a hard crash. Discovered in 2026-05-17 dogfood session."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[6]: agent-ux,bug,context,mcp,pm-cli,regression
created_at: "2026-05-17T05:46:37.065Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-17T08:15:56.156Z"
deadline: "2026-05-18T05:46:37.065Z"
author: claude-code-agent
resolution: "Fixed in 46a225b: stripListProjectionFlags() removes compact/brief/fields/includeBody/include_body before runList/runCalendar; toContextFocusItem hardened to default tags to []; regression test covers all known projection-flag permutations. All 1319 tests pass."
expected_result: "Expected result: closure includes explicit resolution metadata and verifiable delivery evidence."
actual_result: "Actual result: Fixed in 46a225b: stripListProjectionFlags() removes compact/brief/fields/includeBody/include_body before runList/runCalendar; toContextFocusItem hardened to default tags to []; regression test covers all known projection-flag permutations. All 1319 tests pass."
